# --- Infra/deploy creds (used by `alchemy deploy`; NEVER bound to the Worker) ---
# Cloudflare account to deploy to. Required when your creds can see more than one
# account, otherwise Alchemy picks one arbitrarily.
CLOUDFLARE_ACCOUNT_ID=
ALCHEMY_STATE_TOKEN=
ALCHEMY_STAGE=prod
# Required once you add any alchemy.secret binding in alchemy.run.ts.
# Keep it stable across deploys (it encrypts secrets in Alchemy state).
# ALCHEMY_PASSWORD=

# --- Runtime secrets (dev: loaded into c.env via [secrets] required in
# --- wrangler.toml; prod: bound as Worker secrets by alchemy.run.ts) ---
# MY_SECRET=
